[
  "Koo Bon-joon is the chairman of LX Group, whose main subsidiary LG International holds interests in energy, tech, tourism and industrial materials. ",
  "Koo is the second oldest of the Koo brothers of the LG Group, Korea's No. 4 conglomerate. ",
  "The bulk of his fortune is derived from the family's de facto holding company LG Corp.",
  "He led the LG International joint venture with Philips, which became LG Display in 2008 and eventually the world's leading LCD manufacturer. "
